main event: Witnesses in Augusta, Georgia, reported a UFO observation to the Air Force.
interesting points: The report indicates that there were insufficient data for evaluation of the UFO sighting., The initial report was sent to a Colonel for review., The Air Force requested further information via an attached form., The letter was dated March 24, 1967., The witnesses expressed a long-standing interest in UFOs.
witness description: The witnesses expressed interest in UFOs and were attempting to report their observation.
